There's another tree.  And another tree. Wow, following the trees really works.  Tree, tree, tree, tree.

Aah! Gimme that!  Phew!
Nyahh! Oh. Sandy, please. Hellllp meeeee!
I need this!
I need it more.
Eee!

Okay!

WOULD YOU TWO MEN STOP YELLING AT EACH OTHER!!!  WHAT DOES THAT PROVE!!?? IF WE'RE GONNA GET OUT OF THIS, WE GOTTA WORK TOGETHER!

I do not play games!  Quick! Get in the tree house, it's the only safe place left!  We should be protected here.  Hold on!
Is this how we're gonna spend the rest of our lives? Living in fleas instead of water?
SpongeBob! That's it! Water!
Water!

AAAAAAHHH!!!!!
If you two don't mind, could you keep it down to a low rumble?

SpongeBob!
